  <brief_title>Microfracture Technique for Talar Articular Cartilage Lesions With or Without Lateral Ligament Repairment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Microfracture Technique for the Treatment of Articular Cartilage Lesions of the Talus With or Without Lateral Ligament Repairment</official_title>
